(18, 1, '2017-03-28 15:57:51', '2017-03-28 15:57:51', '[av_heading tag=\'h3\' padding=\'10\' heading=\'PATENTS\' color=\'\' style=\'\' custom_font=\'\' size=\'\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'15\' custom_class=\'\' admin_preview_bg=\'\'][/av_heading]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\' admin_preview_bg=\'\']\r\nPatent No. US 9.255,912 (<a href="https://patents.google.com/patent/US9255912B2/en" target="_blank">Link</a>) "Monolithic FBAR-COS structure such as for mass sensing," Feb 9, 2016\r\n\r\nPatent No. US 9,217,727 (<a href="/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/1-1.pdf" target="_blank">PDF</a>), "Systems and methods for single-molecule detection using nanopores," December 22, 2015.\r\n\r\nPatent No. US 9,194,801 B2 (<a href="/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/US9194801.pdf" target="_blank">PDF</a>), "Systems and methods for a DNA-based thermometer," Nov. 24, 2015.\r\n\r\nPatent No. US 8,735,209 B2 (<a href="https://www.bioee.ee.columbia.edu/patents/US8735209.pdf" target="_blank">PDF</a>), "Graphene device including a PVA layer or formed using a PVA layer," May 27, 2014.\r\n\r\nPatent No. US 8,445,893 B2 (<a href="/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/US8445893.pdf" target="_blank">PDF</a>), "High-Performance gate oxides such as for graphene field-effect transistors or carbon nanotubes," May 21, 2013.\r\n\r\nPatent No. US 7,880,551 B2 (<a href="/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/US7880551B2.pdf" target="_blank">PDF</a>) "Systems and methods for distributing a clock signal, " Feb 1, 2011.\r\n\r\nPatent US 7,738,086 B2 (<a href="/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/US7738086.pdf" target="_blank">PDF</a>), "Active CMOS biosensor chip for fluorescent-based detection," Jun. 15, 2010.\r\n\r\nPatent No. US 7,329,968 B2 (<a href="/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/patent1.pdf" target="_blank">PDF</a>), "Charge-Recycling Voltage Domains for Energy-Efficient Low-Voltage Operation of Digital CMOS Circuits," February 12, 2008.\r\n\r\nPatent No. US 7,145,408 B2 (<a href="/wp-content/uploads/2