pplicability in detecting redox-active species from diverse biological samples.\r\n[/av_toggle]\r\n\r\n[/av_toggle_container]', 'Electrochemical camera chip for simultaneous imaging of multiple metabolites in biofilms', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '797-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-05 21:43:46', '2017-04-05 21:43:46', '', 797, 'http://bioee.dev/797-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
